{"tid":1488732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大家咁冇信心，運動會因為一日而玩完？","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T17:39:12.000Z","uid":86828,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9d32f24802e37f1974082ef0d09e9fbdf9f9c239","tid":1488732,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:38:47.000Z","msg":"成日就係度指責大家<br />\n又唔提左五大訴求<br />\n又唔提八百人被捕<br />\n又唔提六位義士<br />\n又唔提爆眼，被行刑式掃射嘅同伴<br />\n又唔記得14年點輸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但事實係<br />\n一路有參與呢運動嘅人<br />\n一定唔會忘記<br />\n而有參與14年傘運嘅人<br />\n更加唔會忘記當年點解會輸</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗再不斷吹風話大家唔記得左<br />\n運動就黎輸等等<br />\n散播失敗主義 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的確，大家有做得唔好嘅野<br />\n例如狗IG單野，我覺得係好撚嚴重<br />\n因為會間接暴露自己身份<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>如果驚大家唔記得嘅話，絕對係可以提醒<br />\n但係唔好不斷散播失敗主義<br />\n當年14年都係有大量嘅失敗主義</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想大家睇下呢篇文<br />\n不厭其麻嘅再推多次<br />\n分析左點解日本民主運動會收皮<br />\n日本社運失敗的歷史<br />\n<br />\n「作者提醒抗爭者，當年日本社運的致命傷，就是過度強調『苦行』，社運人士無論是自己或同路人的要求太高，也不讓人抗爭容下一點輕鬆，不容忍抗爭者可以有一絲快樂。如此思考方法，讓日本社運走入互相批鬥，失去了主流社會支持的死胡同。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=a001a112\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2&h=1fc71df6\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9c319dd195748d116b195e966db84511585e910","tid":1488732,"uid":86828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:07.000Z","msg":"我知有d手足係想大家keep住團火<br />\n所以先講得誇張左<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好唔記得狼來了嘅故事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869050ddbcc76670ec499a6143d476dcdf305f71","tid":1488732,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d277dcbc00123966faa9cf80dd1a8ff26775e09e","tid":1488732,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"最怕自己分化自己"},{"pid":"51df69e4f39b4a62b6a04b544aedc7436add57eb","tid":1488732,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61e0e8ded45df1ccdfbef8d42d5189158e7b822d","tid":1488732,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"對手足<br />\n對巴打<br />\n<br />\n要有信心先得"},{"pid":"6db6af27727022242788ed61887f896ad249ba1d","tid":1488732,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"因為咁少事而話要割嘅話<br />\n<br />\n又話核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af836c60a46e93080d40225a8c6744f17893d06","tid":1488732,"uid":86828